Beatrix the Queen regnant of the Kingdom of the Netherlands announces her abdication in favour of her son, Prince Willem-Alexander, on April 30, 2013. (BBC) (The Telegraph) (AP via ABC News)The inaugural Orwell Day gets underway, to be followed by a month-long Orwell season on BBC Radio 4, while "Politics and the English Language" is to be given away en masse. (The Guardian)